<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>纽约时报 &amp;gt; 美国 &amp;gt; 政治</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/spotlight/on-politics</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 22:00:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>预览加州初选和高风险的州长竞选</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/01/us/politics/california-primary-elections-governor-preview.html</link><description>这个深蓝色州的初选将显示选民对现状有多么愤怒。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 22:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/01/us/politics/california-primary-elections-governor-preview.html</guid></item><item><title>塔拉里科能否赢得德克萨斯州科宁的部分选民的支持？</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/29/us/politics/talarico-cornyn-texas-voters.html</link><description>民主党人希望如此，但有充分的理由对此表示怀疑。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 21:50:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/29/us/politics/talarico-cornyn-texas-voters.html</guid></item><item><title>民主党全国委员会主席、特朗普的 18 亿美元基金和更多政治新闻</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/22/us/politics/dnc-chairman-ken-martin-lutnick-.html</link><description>他专注于内部政治，尽管存在战术争议，但仍建立了忠诚的基础。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 May 2026 21:07:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/22/us/politics/dnc-chairman-ken-martin-lutnick-.html</guid></item><item><title>为什么乔什·夏皮罗的表现不像其他 2028 年潜在候选人</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/18/us/politics/josh-shapiro-pennsylvania-2028.html</link><description>这位宾夕法尼亚州州长对州内的关注与其他可能的总统候选人形成了鲜明对比。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 May 2026 22:37:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/18/us/politics/josh-shapiro-pennsylvania-2028.html</guid></item><item><title>伊朗战争的强烈反对会拯救肯塔基州众议员托马斯·马西吗？</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/15/us/politics/thomas-massie-kentucky-iran.html</link><description>肯塔基州托马斯·马西区的景色。</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 21:18:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/15/us/politics/thomas-massie-kentucky-iran.html</guid></item><item><title>特朗普关于美国财政和伊朗战争的言论指向共和党中期挑战</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/13/us/politics/trump-iran-war-american-finances-republicans-midterms.html</link><description>当被问及是否是出于美国经济困境而达成协议以结束与伊朗的战争时，他回答说：“一点也没有。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 00:42:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/13/us/politics/trump-iran-war-american-finances-republicans-midterms.html</guid></item><item><title>民主党在纽约初选中的表现如何</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/us/politics/nyc-midterms-elections-democrats.html</link><description>建制派和左翼领导人正在为分散在城市各地的众议院席位发生冲突。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 21:17:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/us/politics/nyc-midterms-elections-democrats.html</guid></item><item><title>我们的记者在万斯 2028 年编码之旅期间在爱荷华州看到了什么</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/08/us/politics/jd-vance-iowa-2028.html</link><description>副总统来到该州为弱势的众议院共和党人做竞选演讲，也许还为潜在的总统竞选奠定了一些基础。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 21:19:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/08/us/politics/jd-vance-iowa-2028.html</guid></item><item><title>密歇根州好斗的民主党参议院初选升温</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/06/us/politics/michigan-senate-primary-democrats.html</link><description>攻击四起，著名的民主党人正在选边站队，战斗才刚刚开始。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 22:28:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/06/us/politics/michigan-senate-primary-democrats.html</guid></item><item><title>五月的初选将考验特朗普对共和党的影响力</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/04/us/politics/may-primary-elections-trump-republicans.html</link><description>一系列共和党竞选将考验他对党的控制力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 21:19:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/04/us/politics/may-primary-elections-trump-republicans.html</guid></item></channel></rss>